    "In more complex network environments, neural networks such as long short-term memory and GNNs can effectively extract temporal and spatial features between different types of network nodes and capture the relationships between nodes (Ferriol-Galmés et al., 2022).",
    "Finally, generative AI can automatically learn complex relationships between various elements and play a critical role in network modeling in case of low training costs.",
